{"word":"Tychicus","slug":"tychicus","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tychicus</b> An Asian companion of Paul.<br/> Accompanies Paul from Greece to Asia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=4'>Act 20:4</a><br/> With Paul in Nicopolis<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=3&verse=12'>Tit 3:12</a><br/> With Paul in Rome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=22'>Eph 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=8'>Col 4:8</a><br/> Sent to Ephesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=22'>Eph 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=12'>2Ti 4:12</a><br/> Sent to Colosse<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=8'>Col 4:8</a>"}]}